ASRM_127.Description: Sum of scores of items 12-Lonely, 13-Confused, 14-Cries a lot, 22-Worries about future, 31-Fears doing bad, 33-Feels unloved, 34-Others out to get him/her, 35-Feels worthless, 45-Nervous, tense, 47-Lacks self-confidence, 50-Fearful, anxious, 52-Feels too guilty, 71-Self-conscious, 91-Suicidal thoughts, 103-Unhappy, sad, depressed, 107-Can’t succeed, 112-Worries, 113-Worries about relations with opposite sex. | Calculation = [ASRM_12] + [ASRM_13] + [ASRM_14] + [ASRM_22] + [ASRM_31] + [ASRM_33] + [ASRM_34] + [ASRM_35] + [ASRM_45] + [ASRM_47] + [ASRM_50] + [ASRM_52] + [ASRM_71] + [ASRM_91] + [ASRM_103] + [ASRM_107] + [ASRM_112] + [ASRM_113]

ASRM_128.Description: Sum of scores of items 25-Doesn’t get along, 30-Poor relations with opposite sex, 42-Rather be alone, 48-Not liked, 60-Enjoys little, 65-Refuses to talk, 67-Trouble making friends, 69-Secretive, 111-Withdrawn. | Calculation = [ASRM_25] + [ASRM_30] + [ASRM_42] + [ASRM_48] + [ASRM_60] + [ASRM_65] + [ASRM_67] + [ASRM_69] + [ASRM_111]

ASRM_129.Description: Sum of scores of items 51-Feels dizzy, 54-Tired without good reason, 56a-Aches, pains, 56b-Headaches, 56c-Nausea, feels sick, 56d-Eye problems, 56e-Skin problems, 56f-Stomachaches, 56g-Vomiting, 56h-Heart pounding, 56i-Numbness, 100a-Trouble sleeping. | Calculation = [ASRM_51] + [ASRM_54] + [ASRM_56a] + [ASRM_56b] + [ASRM_56c] + [ASRM_56d1] + [ASRM_56e] + [ASRM_56f] + [ASRM_56g] + [ASRM_56h] + [ASRM_56i] + [ASRM_100a]

ASRM_130.Description: Sum of scores of items 9a-Can’t get mind off thoughts, 18-Harms self, 36-Accident-prone, 40a-Hears sounds, voices, 46a-Twitching, 63-Prefers older people, 66a-Repeats acts, 70a-Sees things, 84a-Strange behavior, 85a-Strange ideas. | Calculation = [ASRM_9a] + [ASRM_18] + [ASRM_36] + [ASRM_40a] + [ASRM_46a] + [ASRM_63] + [ASRM_66a] + [ASRM_70a] + [ASRM_84a] + [ASRM_85a]

ASRM_131.Description: Sum of scores of items 1-Forgetful, 8-Can’t concentrate, 11-Too dependent, 17-Confused, 53-Trouble planning, 59-Fails to finish, 61-Poor work performance, 64-Trouble setting priorities, 78-Trouble making decisions, 101-Skips job, 102-Lacks energy, 105-Disorganized, 108-Loses things, 119-Not good at details, 121-Late for appointments. | Calculation = [ASRM_01] + [ASRM_08] + [ASRM_11] + [ASRM_17] + [ASRM_53] + [ASRM_59] + [ASRM_61] + [ASRM_64] + [ASRM_78] + [ASRM_101] + [ASRM_102] + [ASRM_105] + [ASRM_108] + [ASRM_119] + [ASRM_121]

ASRM_132.Description: Sum of scores of items 3-Argues, 5-Blames others, 16-Mean to others, 28-Gets along badly with family, 37-Gets in fights, 55-Mood swings between elation and depression, 57-Attacks, 68-Screams a lot, 81-Changeable behavior, 86-Stubborn, sullen, irritable, 87-Mood changes, 95-Hot temper, 97-Threatens people, 116-Easily upset, 118-Impatient. | Calculation = [ASRM_03] + [ASRM_05] + [ASRM_16] + [ASRM_28] + [ASRM_37] + [ASRM_55] + [ASRM_57] + [ASRM_68] + [ASRM_81] + [ASRM_86] + [ASRM_87] + [ASRM_95] + [ASRM_97] + [ASRM_116] + [ASRM_118]

ASRM_133.Description: Sum of scores of items 6a-Use drugs, 20-Damages own things, 23-Breaks rules, 26-Lacks guilt, 39-Bad friends, 41-Impulsive, 43-Lying, cheating, 76-Irresponsible, 82-Steals, 90-Gets drunk, 92a-Trouble with the law, 114-Fails to pay debts, 117-Trouble managing money, 122-Trouble keeping jobs. | Calculation = [ASRM_06a] + [ASRM_20] + [ASRM_23] + [ASRM_26] + [ASRM_39] + [ASRM_41] + [ASRM_43] + [ASRM_76] + [ASRM_82] + [ASRM_90] + [ASRM_92a] + [ASRM_114] + [ASRM_117] + [ASRM_122]

ASRM_134.Description: Sum of scores of items 7-Brags, 19-Demands attention, 74-Showing off, clowning, 93-Talks too much, 94-Teases a lot, 104-Loud. | Calculation = [ASRM_07] + [ASRM_19] + [ASRM_74] + [ASRM_93] + [ASRM_94] + [ASRM_104]

ASRM_135.Description: Sum of scores of items 10-Can’t sit still, 21-Damages other’s things, 24-Doesn’t eat well, 27-Jealous, 29a-Fears, 32-Must be perfect, 38-Poor relations with neighbors, 44-Overwhelmed by responsibilities, 58a-Picks skin, 62-Clumsy, 72-Worries about family, 75-Too shy, 77a-Sleeps more than other people, 79a-Speech problem, 83-Easily bored, 89-Rushes into things, 96-Thinks about sex, 99-Dislikes staying in one place, 110-Wishes to be opposite sex, 115-Restless, fidgety, 120-Drives too fast. | Calculation = [ASRM_10] + [ASRM_21] + [ASRM_24] + [ASRM_27] + [ASRM_29a] + [ASRM_32] + [ASRM_38] + [ASRM_44] + [ASRM_58a] + [ASRM_62] + [ASRM_72] + [ASRM_75] + [ASRM_77a] + [ASRM_79a] + [ASRM_83] + [ASRM_89] + [ASRM_96] + [ASRM_99] + [ASRM_110] + [ASRM_115] + [ASRM_120]

ASRM_136.Description: “Critical” items were determined by a group of highly experienced psychiatrists and psychologists from 10 cultures who identified ASEBA adult problem items that are very consistent with DSM-IV diagnostic categories. Sum of scores of items 14-Cries, 6a-Uses drugs, 8-Can’t concentrate, 9a-Can’t get mind off thoughts, 10-Can’t sit still, 16-Mean to others, 18-Harms self, 21-Damages other’s things, 40a-Hears sounds, voices, 55-Mood swings, 57-Attacks, 66a-Repeats acts, 70a-Sees things, 84a-Strange behavior, 90-Gets drunk, 91-Suicidal thoughts, 92a-Trouble with the law, 97-Threatens people, 103-Unhappy, sad, depressed. | Calculation = [ASRM_14] + [ASRM_91] + [ASRM_103] + [ASRM_9a] + [ASRM_18] + [ASRM_40a] + [ASRM_66a] + [ASRM_70a] + [ASRM_84a] + [ASRM_08] + [ASRM_16] + [ASRM_55] + [ASRM_57] + [ASRM_97] + [ASRM_06a] + [ASRM_90] + [ASRM_92a] +[ASRM_10] + [ASRM_21]

ASRM_137.Description: Sum of Anxious/Depressed, Withdrawn, and Somatic Complaints Subscores. This grouping is called “Internalizing,” because it comprises problems that are mainly within the self. | Calculation = [ASRM_127] + [ASRM_128] + [ASRM_129]

ASRM_138.Description: Sum of Aggressive Behavior, Rule-Breaking Behavior, and Intrusive Subscores. The problems comprising the Externalizing grouping mainly involve conflicts with other people and with social mores. | Calculation = [ASRM_132] + [ASRM_133] + [ASRM_134]

ASRM_139.Description: Sum of Thought Problems, Attention Problems, and Other Problems. | Calculation = [ASRM_130] + [ASRM_131] + [ASRM_135]

ASRM_140.Description: Sum of Thought Problems, Attention Problems, Other Problems, Internalizing Behaviors and Externalizing Behaviors. A participant’s Total Problems score can range from 0 (if the respondent scored every problem 0) to 246 (if the respondent scored every problem 2). | Calculation = [ASRM_137] + [ASRM_138] + [ASRM_139]
